  m_text: My name is Bane. I am part of a pirate band called The Salty Shells. I
    can play the drums and I can sing but I cannot play the saxophone or the keyboard.
    My friend Hook plays the guitar but he can't sing. Slash plays the saxophone
    and is a great dancer and Ripley plays the keyboard and he is a great dancer
    too. We often perform together at the harbor.
