  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Bane: "Detective... Thank you for being so kind to me. I have to tell
    you the truth.

    I was the pirate who took the red sunglasses, the blue cap
    and the black jacket. But when I arrived at Mr Whinnyham''s shop, the door was
    already open and everything was a mess. I love clothes and I could not resist
    taking them. I promise I will pay Mr Whinnyham back.

    There is something
    more important. I remember a strange letter lying on the floor. The letter smelled
    familiar. It smelled like an old dusty cellar room underneath the Academy. years
    ago, my band practised in a secret room there. We entered it through the library.
    Maybe you should investigate the Academy Library next."'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0c5df167dbcd31e47b3956228346cfe1, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 8114860532473945583, guid: 0c5df167dbcd31e47b3956228346cfe1, type: 2}
